                            <comment id="15683936" author="jbonofre" created="Mon, 21 Nov 2016 15:59:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the report. I will convert the scientific notation in bytes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15683942" author="crcsmnky" created="Mon, 21 Nov 2016 16:01:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have a simple patch ready, just involves casting returned value as Number and then converting to longValue. Should I submit or hold off?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15683970" author="jbonofre" created="Mon, 21 Nov 2016 16:10:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s what I had in mind. If you can, please submit a PR, I will review. Thanks !&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15683974" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 21 Nov 2016 16:12:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user crcsmnky opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/incubator-beam/pull/1394&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/incubator-beam/pull/1394&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEAM-1018&quot; title=&quot;getEstimatedSizeBytes fails with large MongoDB collection sizes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;BEAM-1018&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;BEAM-1018&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: updated getEstimatedSizeBytes to use Number.longValue()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Updated BoundedMongoDbSource.getEstimatesSizeBytes to use more generic `Number` class and then return `longValue()`. For smaller collections the `size` is returned as Long but for larger collections, the `size` can be returned using scientific notation.&lt;/p&gt;



